/>&lt;<a href=\"https://therecord.media/china-cyber-agency-claims-us-interference-volt-typhoon-research\" title=\"Follow external link\" class=\"exlink\" target=\"_blank\">https://therecord.media/china-cyber-agency-claims-us-interference-volt-typhoon-research</a>&gt;<br />&lt;<a href=\"https://thehackernews.com/2024/10/china-accuses-us-of-fabricating-volt.html\" title=\"Follow external link\" class=\"exlink\" target=\"_blank\">https://thehackernews.com/2024/10/china-accuses-us-of-fabricating-volt.html</a>&gt;<br />&lt;<a href=\"https://www.securityweek.com/china-admitted-to-us-that-it-conducted-volt-typhoon-attacks-report/\" title=\"Follow external link\" class=\"exlink\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.securityweek.com/china-admitted-to-us-that-it-conducted-volt-typhoon-attacks-report/</a>&gt;<br />&lt;<a href=\"https://therecord.media/china-typhoon-hackers-nsa-fbi-response\" title=\"Follow external link\" class=\"exlink\" target=\"_blank\">https://therecord.media/china-typhoon-hackers-nsa-fbi-response</a>&gt;</td></tr>\n</table>\n<p>Last change to this card: 16 August 2025</p>\n<p>Download this actor card in <a href=\"/cgi-bin/getcard.cgi?g=Volt%20Typhoon&o=p\" title=\"Download this card in PDF format\" class=\"inlink\">PDF</a> or <a href=\"/cgi-bin/getcard.cgi?g=Volt%20Typhoon&o=j\" title=\"Download this card in JSON format\" class=\"inlink\">JSON</a> format</p>\n<div class=\"backtotop\"><a href=\"#top\" title=\"Back to the top\" class=\"inlink\">&uarr;</a></div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n<table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\">\n<tr><td width=\"80%\" rowspan=\"4\" valign=\"top\">\n<p>Infrastructure and Security Department<br />\nElectronic Transactions Development Agency</p>\n<h3>Follow us on</h3>\n<a href=\"https://facebook.com/ETDA.Thailand\"><img src=\"/img/icon-facebook.png\" alt=\"Facebook\" title=\"Follow us on Facebook\" /></a>\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/etda_thailand\"><img src=\"/img/icon-twitter.png\" alt=\"Twitter\" title=\"Follow us on Twitter\" /></a>\n</td><